text:
The relay is Domain hardware on a dead orbit, forty years past its last service flag. Its buffer holds decades of nothing and, from twenty days ago, fragments of a distress record.

//BUFFER 4 OF 7// ...read it like a survey return, but the mass is wrong, the mass must be wrong...

//BUFFER 5 OF 7// ...took the drive section whole. Not a shot fired at the crew spaces. It is not interested in...

//BUFFER 7 OF 7// ...course change again. Toward the deep field. It knows where it is going.

You don't know if this was the Threat the Broceliande Station's records spoke of.
